			<div class="content" id="post-content-4835632">
									

<p>I am so utterly confused. So 049 sucks the blood out of a tiny mosquito, using a syringe <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">which the needle would obviously be far too big to prod a tiny mosquito with anyway, to be completely honest</span> and replaces the blood with something else. Then the mosquito is brought to life but now it is TALKING and it thinks it’s some girl named Leslie who’s been dead for 200 years!? I am so confused. What is going on? I have so many questions and no idea where to find the answer. I don’t even know if I wanna find out the answer because this is also bizarre.</p>
<p>So 049 not only figures out how to bring the dead back to life without them being zombies, but he somehow learns how to transplant past souls into insignificant insects? I am so lost here. Where does he get the ability to transplant human souls/consciousness? Where did he even get the soul from? How did he acquire this new power?</p>

							</div>

								
